OL,6,FSalah said he signed "because I think
OL,7,Fwe have a chance to win other trophies
OL,8,Fand enjoy my football".
OL,10,FThe forward, has so far scored 32 goal
OL,11,Fin 45 appearances across all
OL,12,Fcompetitions for Arne Slot's team, and
OL,13,Fis current top scorer in the Premier
OL,14,FLeague with 27.
OL,16,FHe told the club website: "Of course
OL,17,FI'm very excited. We have a great team
OL,18,Fnow. Before also we had a great team.
OL,19,FBut I signed because I think we have a
OL,20,Fchance to win other trophies and enjoy
OL,21,Fmy football.
