OL,6,F"It's great, I had my best years here.
OL,7,FI played eight years, hopefully it's
OL,8,Fgoing to be 10. Enjoying my life here,
OL,9,Fenjoying my football. I had the best
OL,10,Fyears in my career.
OL,12,F"I would like to say to (the fans), I
OL,13,Fam very, very happy to be here. I
OL,14,Fsigned here because I believe we can
OL,15,Fwin a lot of big trophies together.
OL,17,F"Keep supporting us and we'll give it
OL,18,Four best, and hopefully in the future
OL,19,Fwe're going to win more trophies."
