OL,6,FSporting director Richard Hughes has
OL,7,Fspent a large amount of his time
OL,8,Fworking on the negotiations, in
OL,9,Faddition to those involving Virgil van
OL,10,FDijk and Trent Alexander-Arnold who
OL,11,Fare also in their final three months.
OL,13,FBut Slot admits it also required the
OL,14,Ffinancial backing of owners Fenway
OL,15,FSports Group to get it over the line
OL,16,Fafter deviating from their policy of
OL,17,Fnot handing players over 30 lucrative
OL,18,Fnew contracts, with a cut in the
OL,19,Fforward's reported #350,000-a-week
OL,20,Fwages never on the agenda in
OL,21,Fdiscussions.
