OL,6,F"First of all, it's Mo's choice and
OL,7,Fhis agent's choice and what he wants.
OL,8,FSecond of all, the club; FSG, Richard,
OL,9,FMichael Edwards (FSG's football chief
OL,10,Fexecutive) put a lot of effort to
OL,11,Finfluence that," said Slot.
OL,13,F"Effort mostly means money ` but also
OL,14,Feffort, not only money.
OL,16,F"It gives a positive vibe to the club,
OL,17,Fmaybe a positive vibe we might not
OL,18,Fneed but it's always good to have
OL,19,Fpositive vibes instead of negative
OL,20,Fvibes.
