OL,6,F"If you want to sign new players or
OL,7,Fplayers who want to extend here, it is
OL,8,Falways a positive to see one of our
OL,9,Fstar players over the last seven or
OL,10,Feight years has made the choice to
OL,11,Fextend his contract.
OL,13,F"It also shows maybe how ambitious
OL,14,Fthis club is: not only Mo, but the
