OL,6,FSalah arrived at Anfield in the summer
OL,7,Fof 2017 and has enjoyed a hugely
OL,8,Fsuccessful spell in his eight years on
OL,9,FMerseyside, where he has won several
OL,10,Fmajor honours including the Premier
OL,11,FLeague, Champions League and FA Cup.
OL,13,FHis goalscoring prowess has been
OL,14,Fintegral for Liverpool's success in
OL,15,Fthat time, earning him three Premier
OL,16,FLeague Golden Boot awards, and he is
OL,17,Fthe third-highest all-time scorer in
OL,18,FLiverpool history with 243 goals in
OL,19,F394 appearances.
